    <!--
        TurtleLauncher Color Theme — v11 "Aurora" repaint
        ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
        Replaces the old green-on-AMOLED-black theme with the teal/purple/
        pink palette from the brand mockup (turtle mascot + wordmark
        gradient: "Turtle" teal → "Launcher" purple).

        Background   #0B0F14   Surface     #12161F   Surface Light #1A1F2B
        Primary      #00F0D1   Secondary   #A78BFA   Accent        #FF71CE
        Highlight    #FFD166   Success     #4ADE80   Error         #F87171
        Text Primary #FFFFFF   Text Secondary #6E7681

        Gradients (used by GradientDrawables / Compose brushes, not single
        colors, so they're not @color entries — kept here for reference):
          Aurora Flow  : #00F0D1 → #A78BFA
          Neon Dream   : #A78BFA → #FF71CE
          Ocean Breeze : #00C2FF → #00F0D1
          Sunset Glow  : #FF71CE → #FFD166
          Void Pulse   : #5B2186 → #0EA5E9

        HUD stat colors (FPS/RAM/CPU/Ping) are project-spec and intentionally
        left untouched by this repaint.
        ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    -->

